{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037120/extras/logo.png?t=1737181986\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <strong>Mercenaries of War</strong>, an online hardcore PvP survival game with <strong>permanent death</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep yourself protected by buying weapons and stocking up on bullets. If you die, your character is permanently dead and you will have to start over fresh. You can also set a backfire which will fire a certain amount of bullets back in defense in a chance to kill your attacker. Attract too much heat and it's off to the slammer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join a growing community and engage in crew wars, 4-player robberies and show who's boss. Wipe out your rival crews! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start your initiation as a <strong>Mercenary of War</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Remember, Money is Power, but so are Bullets.</i></strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737181986","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037120/page.bg.jpg?t=1737181986","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037120/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737181986","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037120/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737181986","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"MMO","id":20},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":null},"detailed_description"